!                          Main magnets                                 !


!-----------------------------------------------------------------------!


! yoke inside
!R          ! D-F unit, yoke outside


ANID = +0.0314770265359;  ! angle (rho = 70 m)
!S          ! F-D unit, yoke outside


!T          ! F-D unit, yoke inside

KI0D =  1.0;
!U          ! D-F unit, yoke inside



KI1D = -0.05872278;


CF001 = 1; ! Correction Factor for Backleg windings

KI2D =  0.0;

CS001 = (1-CF001)*(0.0313548265359+0.0314770265359); ! Correction Strength
KI3D =  0.0;


KI4D =  0.0;

KI5D =  0.0;



! yoke outside

ANED = +0.0314770265359;  ! angle (rho = 70 m)

KE0D =  1.0;

PR.BHT000001.corr1  : HKICKER, KICK=CS001/5; ! Back leg windings
KE1D = -0.05872278;


KE2D =  0.0;

KE3D =  0.0;

KE4D =  0.0;

KE5D =  0.0;

PR.BHT000001.corr2  : HKICKER, KICK=CS001/5; ! Back leg windings



!-----------------------------------------------------------------------!

!                          Junction between half-units                  !

!-----------------------------------------------------------------------!

LJ   :=  0.0025  ;    ! Length of junction F-D

j1       : SBEND,L=LJ,K1=0,K2=0;

j2       : SBEND,L=LJ,K1=0,K2=0;



!-----------------------------------------------------------------------!

!                          Pole face windings                           !

!-----------------------------------------------------------------------!

! The bending magnets may contain multipoles, defined

! by parameters PFKI<n><p>, where n = 1,2,3,4 and p = F or D.

! These multipoles are introduced as thin lenses at the

! entrance and exit of each half-unit.

! The bending magnets can have the yoke inside or outside; and the

! multipole names ends in the letter: i or e, respectively.



mpfi1    : MULTIPOLE, knl:={0,PFKI1F,PFKI2F,PFKI3F,PFKI4F,PFKI5F};

mpdi1    : MULTIPOLE, knl:={0,PFKI1D,PFKI2D,PFKI3D,PFKI4D,PFKI5D};

mpfe1    : MULTIPOLE, knl:={0,PFKI1F,PFKI2F,PFKI3F,PFKI4F,PFKI5F};

mpde1    : MULTIPOLE, knl:={0,PFKI1D,PFKI2D,PFKI3D,PFKI4D,PFKI5D};



mpfi2    : MULTIPOLE, knl:={0,PFKI1F,PFKI2F,PFKI3F,PFKI4F,PFKI5F};

mpdi2    : MULTIPOLE, knl:={0,PFKI1D,PFKI2D,PFKI3D,PFKI4D,PFKI5D};

mpfe2    : MULTIPOLE, knl:={0,PFKI1F,PFKI2F,PFKI3F,PFKI4F,PFKI5F};

mpde2    : MULTIPOLE, knl:={0,PFKI1D,PFKI2D,PFKI3D,PFKI4D,PFKI5D};



!-----------------------------------------------------------------------!

!                          Main magnets                                 !

!-----------------------------------------------------------------------!

!R          ! D-F unit, yoke outside

!S          ! F-D unit, yoke outside

!T          ! F-D unit, yoke inside

!U          ! D-F unit, yoke inside



CF001 = 1; ! Correction Factor for Backleg windings

CS001 = (1-CF001)*(0.0313548265359+0.0314770265359); ! Correction Strength

PR.BHT000001.corr1  : HKICKER, KICK=CS001/5; ! Back leg windings

PR.BHT000001.corr2  : HKICKER, KICK=CS001/5; ! Back leg windings

PR.BHT000001.corr3  : HKICKER, KICK=CS001/5; ! Back leg windings

PR.BHT000001.corr4  : HKICKER, KICK=CS001/5; ! Back leg windings
PR.BHT000001.corr3  : HKICKER, KICK=CS001/5; ! Back leg windings


PR.BHT000001.corr5  : HKICKER, KICK=CS001/5; ! Back leg windings

PR.BHT000001.corr4  : HKICKER, KICK=CS001/5; ! Back leg windings



PR.BHT000001.FINFF1 : SBEND,L=(LF+DLF)/2,E1=EF,K1:=KI1F*CF001,K2:=KI2F*CF001,ANGLE=ANIF*REV/2;
PR.BHT000001.corr5  : HKICKER, KICK=CS001/5; ! Back leg windings




PR.BHT000001.FINFF1 : SBEND,L=(LF+DLF)/2,E1=EF,K1:=KI1F*CF001,K2:=KI2F*CF001,ANGLE=ANIF*REV/2;

PR.BHT000001.FINFF2 : SBEND,L=(LF+DLF)/2,E2=EF,K1:=KI1F*CF001,K2:=KI2F*CF001,ANGLE=ANIF*REV/2;

PR.BHT000001.FINFF2 : SBEND,L=(LF+DLF)/2,E2=EF,K1:=KI1F*CF001,K2:=KI2F*CF001,ANGLE=ANIF*REV/2;

PR.BHT000001.DINDD1 : SBEND,L=(LD+DLD)/2,E1=ED,K1:=KI1D*CF001,K2:=KI2D*CF001,ANGLE=ANID*REV/2;

PR.BHT000001.DINDD1 : SBEND,L=(LD+DLD)/2,E1=ED,K1:=KI1D*CF001,K2:=KI2D*CF001,ANGLE=ANID*REV/2;

PR.BHT000001.DINDD2 : SBEND,L=(LD+DLD)/2,E2=ED,K1:=KI1D*CF001,K2:=KI2D*CF001,ANGLE=ANID*REV/2;

PR.BHT000001.DINDD2 : SBEND,L=(LD+DLD)/2,E2=ED,K1:=KI1D*CF001,K2:=KI2D*CF001,ANGLE=ANID*REV/2;

! The bending magnets may contain multipoles, defined

! These multipoles are introduced as thin lenses at the

! entrance and exit of each half-unit.

! multipole names ends in the letter: i or e, respectively.

PR.BHT000003 : SEQUENCE, refer = CENTRE,  L = 5.00318530718;  ! F-D unit, yoke inside
!-----------------------------------------------------------------------!


! The bending magnets may contain multipoles, defined
 PR.BHR000004.mpde1  : mpde1,  AT = 0.2985726;


! by parameters PFKI<n><p>, where n = 1,2,3,4 and p = F or D.

! These multipoles are introduced as thin lenses at the

! entrance and exit of each half-unit.

! The bending magnets can have the yoke inside or outside; and the

 PR.BHR000004.DEXDD1         , AT = 0.8497726;
! multipole names ends in the letter: i or e, respectively.




mpfi1    : MULTIPOLE, knl:={0,PFKI1F,PFKI2F,PFKI3F,PFKI4F,PFKI5F};

 PR.BHR000004.DEXDD1         , AT = 0.8497726;

 PR.BHR000004.corr2          , AT = 1.4009726;

 PR.BHR000004.corr2          , AT = 1.4009726;

ptc_twiss_beta_macro(location): macro={

  ptc_create_universe;

  ptc_create_layout,time=false,model=2,method=6,nst=3,exact;

  select,flag=ptc_twiss, clear;

  select,flag=ptc_twiss, column=name, s,x,px,beta11,beta22,alfa11,alfa22,mu1,mu2;

  ptc_twiss,closed_orbit;

  betax_ref=table(ptc_twiss,location,beta11);

  betay_ref=table(ptc_twiss,location,beta22);

  ptc_end;

};



ptc_twiss_tune_macro: macro={

  ptc_create_universe;

  ptc_create_layout, time=false, model=2, exact=true, method=6, nst=5;

  ptc_twiss, closed_orbit, table=ptc_twiss,icase=56,no=2,summary_table=ptc_twiss_summary,file="./LHC_injection_bump_2012.out";

  qx0=table(ptc_twiss_summary,Q1);

  qy0=table(ptc_twiss_summary,Q2);

  value, qx0, qy0;

  ptc_end;

};



ptc_chrom_macro: macro={

  ptc_create_universe;

  ptc_create_layout,time=false,model=2,method=6,nst=3,exact=true;

  select_ptc_normal, q1=0, q2=0;

  select_ptc_normal,dq1=1,dq2=1;

  select_ptc_normal,dq1=2,dq2=2;

  select_ptc_normal,dq1=3,dq2=3;

  ptc_normal,closed_orbit,normal,icase=5,no=4;

  ptc_end;

  qx0 =table(normal_results,value,1);

  qx1 =table(normal_results,value,3);

  qx2 =table(normal_results,value,5);

  qx3 =table(normal_results,value,7);

  qy0 =table(normal_results,value,2);

  qy1 =table(normal_results,value,4);

  qy2 =table(normal_results,value,6);

  qy3 =table(normal_results,value,8);

  value, qx0, qx1, qx2, qx3, qy0, qy1, qy2, qy3;

};

call, file='./multipole_coefficients_injection_2016.dat';

ptc_twiss_beta_macro(location): macro={


  ptc_create_universe;

  ptc_create_layout,time=false,model=2,method=6,nst=3,exact;



  select,flag=ptc_twiss, clear;
endedit;


  select,flag=ptc_twiss, column=name, s,x,px,beta11,beta22,alfa11,alfa22,mu1,mu2;

++++++ info: seqedit - number of elements installed:  0
  ptc_twiss,closed_orbit;
++++++ info: seqedit - number of elements moved:      0

++++++ info: seqedit - number of elements removed:    0
  betax_ref=table(ptc_twiss,location,beta11);



  betay_ref=table(ptc_twiss,location,beta22);
/******************************************************************


  ptc_end;
 * SS78


};
 ******************************************************************/

  ptc_twiss, closed_orbit, table=ptc_twiss,icase=56,no=2,summary_table=ptc_twiss_summary,file="./LHC_injection_bump_2012.out";
++++++ info: seqedit - number of elements moved:      0

call, file="./lattice/scripts/macros.ptc";

ptc_twiss_beta_macro(location): macro={

  ptc_create_universe;

  ptc_create_layout,time=false,model=2,method=6,nst=3,exact;

  select,flag=ptc_twiss, clear;

  select,flag=ptc_twiss, column=name, s,x,px,beta11,beta22,alfa11,alfa22,mu1,mu2;

  ptc_twiss,closed_orbit;

  betax_ref=table(ptc_twiss,location,beta11);

  betay_ref=table(ptc_twiss,location,beta22);

  ptc_end;

};



ptc_twiss_tune_macro: macro={

  ptc_create_universe;

  ptc_create_layout, time=false, model=2, exact=true, method=6, nst=5;

  ptc_twiss, closed_orbit, table=ptc_twiss,icase=56,no=2,summary_table=ptc_twiss_summary,file="./LHC_injection_bump_2012.out";

  qx0=table(ptc_twiss_summary,Q1);

  qy0=table(ptc_twiss_summary,Q2);

  value, qx0, qy0;

/******************************************************************
  ptc_end;


 * SS07
};


 ******************************************************************/


seqedit, sequence=PS07;


ptc_chrom_macro: macro={

  ptc_create_universe;

  ptc_create_layout,time=false,model=2,method=6,nst=3,exact=true;

  select_ptc_normal, q1=0, q2=0;

  select_ptc_normal,dq1=1,dq2=1;
remove, element=PR.QLT07;


  select_ptc_normal,dq1=2,dq2=2;

  select_ptc_normal,dq1=3,dq2=3;

  ptc_normal,closed_orbit,normal,icase=5,no=4;

endedit;
  ptc_end;


  qx0 =table(normal_results,value,1);

++++++ info: seqedit - number of elements installed:  0
  qx1 =table(normal_results,value,3);
++++++ info: seqedit - number of elements moved:      0
++++++ info: seqedit - number of elements removed:    1


/******************************************************************


  qx2 =table(normal_results,value,5);
 * SS15


  qx3 =table(normal_results,value,7);
 ******************************************************************/


  qy0 =table(normal_results,value,2);
seqedit, sequence=PS15;


  qy1 =table(normal_results,value,4);

  qy2 =table(normal_results,value,6);

  qy3 =table(normal_results,value,8);
remove, element=PR.QNT15;


  value, qx0, qx1, qx2, qx3, qy0, qy1, qy2, qy3;

};
endedit;

++++++ info: seqedit - number of elements moved:      0
++++++ info: seqedit - number of elements removed:    1

ptc_twiss_beta_macro(location): macro={

  ptc_create_universe;

  ptc_create_layout,time=false,model=2,method=6,nst=3,exact;

  select,flag=ptc_twiss, clear;

  select,flag=ptc_twiss, column=name, s,x,px,beta11,beta22,alfa11,alfa22,mu1,mu2;

  ptc_twiss,closed_orbit;

  betax_ref=table(ptc_twiss,location,beta11);

  betay_ref=table(ptc_twiss,location,beta22);

  ptc_end;

};



ptc_twiss_tune_macro: macro={

  ptc_create_universe;

  ptc_create_layout, time=false, model=2, exact=true, method=6, nst=5;

  ptc_twiss, closed_orbit, table=ptc_twiss,icase=56,no=2,summary_table=ptc_twiss_summary,file="./LHC_injection_bump_2012.out";

  qx0=table(ptc_twiss_summary,Q1);

  qy0=table(ptc_twiss_summary,Q2);

  value, qx0, qy0;

  ptc_end;

};



ptc_chrom_macro: macro={

  ptc_create_universe;

  ptc_create_layout,time=false,model=2,method=6,nst=3,exact=true;

  select_ptc_normal, q1=0, q2=0;

  select_ptc_normal,dq1=1,dq2=1;

  select_ptc_normal,dq1=2,dq2=2;

  select_ptc_normal,dq1=3,dq2=3;

  ptc_normal,closed_orbit,normal,icase=5,no=4;

  ptc_end;

  qx0 =table(normal_results,value,1);

  qx1 =table(normal_results,value,3);

  qx2 =table(normal_results,value,5);

  qx3 =table(normal_results,value,7);

  qy0 =table(normal_results,value,2);

  qy1 =table(normal_results,value,4);

  qy2 =table(normal_results,value,6);

  qy3 =table(normal_results,value,8);

  value, qx0, qx1, qx2, qx3, qy0, qy1, qy2, qy3;

};

call, file="./lattice/scripts/macros.ptc";
 Now PTC

ptc_create_layout, time=false, model=2, exact=true, method=6, nst=5;

ptc_twiss_beta_macro(location): macro={

  ptc_create_universe;

  ptc_create_layout,time=false,model=2,method=6,nst=3,exact;

  select,flag=ptc_twiss, clear;

  select,flag=ptc_twiss, column=name, s,x,px,beta11,beta22,alfa11,alfa22,mu1,mu2;

  ptc_twiss,closed_orbit;

  betax_ref=table(ptc_twiss,location,beta11);

  betay_ref=table(ptc_twiss,location,beta22);

  ptc_end;

};



ptc_twiss_tune_macro: macro={

  ptc_create_universe;

  ptc_create_layout, time=false, model=2, exact=true, method=6, nst=5;

  ptc_twiss, closed_orbit, table=ptc_twiss,icase=56,no=2,summary_table=ptc_twiss_summary,file="./LHC_injection_bump_2012.out";

  qx0=table(ptc_twiss_summary,Q1);

  qy0=table(ptc_twiss_summary,Q2);

  value, qx0, qy0;

  ptc_end;

};



ptc_chrom_macro: macro={

  ptc_create_universe;

  ptc_create_layout,time=false,model=2,method=6,nst=3,exact=true;

  select_ptc_normal, q1=0, q2=0;

  select_ptc_normal,dq1=1,dq2=1;

  select_ptc_normal,dq1=2,dq2=2;

  select_ptc_normal,dq1=3,dq2=3;

  ptc_normal,closed_orbit,normal,icase=5,no=4;

  ptc_end;

  qx0 =table(normal_results,value,1);

  qx1 =table(normal_results,value,3);

  qx2 =table(normal_results,value,5);

  qx3 =table(normal_results,value,7);

  qy0 =table(normal_results,value,2);

  qy1 =table(normal_results,value,4);

  qy2 =table(normal_results,value,6);

  qy3 =table(normal_results,value,8);

  value, qx0, qx1, qx2, qx3, qy0, qy1, qy2, qy3;

};

call, file='./multipole_coefficients_injection_2016.dat';
